{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":603,"text":"I know a man who soars above the city every night."},{"time":6465,"text":"In his dreams, he twirls and swirls"},{"time":9459,"text":"with his toes kissing the Earth."},{"time":12326,"text":"Everything has motion, he claims,"},{"time":15140,"text":"even a body as paralyzed as his own."},{"time":19982,"text":"This man is my father."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24812,"text":"Three years ago, when I found out"},{"time":26713,"text":"that my father had suffered a severe stroke"},{"time":29300,"text":"in his brain stem,"},{"time":31426,"text":"I walked into his room in the ICU"},{"time":34900,"text":"at the Montreal Neurological Institute"},{"time":37884,"text":"and found him lying deathly still,"},{"time":40527,"text":"tethered to a breathing machine."},{"time":43463,"text":"Paralysis had closed over his body slowly,"},{"time":47894,"text":"beginning in his toes, then legs,"},{"time":49965,"text":"torso, fingers and arms."},{"time":52495,"text":"It made its way up his neck,"},{"time":54700,"text":"cutting off his ability to breathe,"},{"time":56905,"text":"and stopped just beneath the eyes."},{"time":61382,"text":"He never lost consciousness."},{"time":63553,"text":"Rather, he watched from within"},{"time":66140,"text":"as his body shut down,"},{"time":68446,"text":"limb by limb,"},{"time":70583,"text":"muscle by muscle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73542,"text":"In that ICU room, I walked up to my father's body,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":78100,"text":"and with a quivering voice and through tears,"},{"time":81699,"text":"I began reciting the alphabet."},{"time":85112,"text":"A, B, C, D, E, F, G,"},{"time":91010,"text":"H, I, J, K."},{"time":95140,"text":"At K, he blinked his eyes."},{"time":98092,"text":"I began again."},{"time":100246,"text":"A, B, C, D, E, F, G,"},{"time":104740,"text":"H, I."},{"time":106750,"text":"He blinked again at the letter I,"},{"time":109888,"text":"then at T, then at R, and A:"},{"time":113880,"text":"Kitra."},{"time":115727,"text":"He said \"Kitra, my beauty, don't cry."},{"time":119685,"text":"This is a blessing.\""},{"time":124140,"text":"There was no audible voice, but my father"},{"time":126795,"text":"called out my name powerfully."},{"time":129843,"text":"Just 72 hours after his stroke,"},{"time":132935,"text":"he had already embraced"},{"time":134690,"text":"the totality of his condition."},{"time":138165,"text":"Despite his extreme physical state,"},{"time":140665,"text":"he was completely present with me,"},{"time":143621,"text":"guiding, nurturing,"},{"time":146253,"text":"and being my father as much"},{"time":148503,"text":"if not more than ever before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151739,"text":"Locked-in syndrome"},{"time":153302,"text":"is many people's worst nightmare."},{"time":156703,"text":"In French, it's sometimes called"},{"time":159111,"text":"\"maladie de l'emmur√© vivant.\""},{"time":161191,"text":"Literally, \"walled-in-alive disease.\""},{"time":166512,"text":"For many people, perhaps most,"},{"time":168267,"text":"paralysis is an unspeakable horror,"},{"time":171799,"text":"but my father's experience"},{"time":174140,"text":"losing every system of his body"},{"time":176511,"text":"was not an experience of feeling trapped,"},{"time":179572,"text":"but rather of turning the psyche inwards,"},{"time":183733,"text":"dimming down the external chatter,"},{"time":186928,"text":"facing the recesses of his own mind,"},{"time":189853,"text":"and in that place,"},{"time":191690,"text":"falling in love with life and body anew."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196470,"text":"As a rabbi and spiritual man"},{"time":199166,"text":"dangling between mind and body, life and death,"},{"time":203280,"text":"the paralysis opened up a new awareness for him."},{"time":207807,"text":"He realized he no longer needed to look"},{"time":210221,"text":"beyond the corporeal world"},{"time":213250,"text":"in order to find the divine."},{"time":216499,"text":"\"Paradise is in this body."},{"time":220388,"text":"It's in this world,\" he said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":224150,"text":"I slept by my father's side for the first four months,"},{"time":228006,"text":"tending as much as I could"},{"time":230120,"text":"to his every discomfort,"},{"time":232765,"text":"understanding the deep \nhuman psychological fear"},{"time":236115,"text":"of not being able to call out for help."},{"time":239600,"text":"My mother, sisters, brother and I,"},{"time":243326,"text":"we surrounded him in a cocoon of healing."},{"time":247690,"text":"We became his mouthpiece,"},{"time":249790,"text":"spending hours each day reciting the alphabet"},{"time":253619,"text":"as he whispered back sermons"},{"time":255981,"text":"and poetry with blinks of his eye."},{"time":259650,"text":"His room, it became our temple of healing."},{"time":265104,"text":"His bedside became a site for those"},{"time":267826,"text":"seeking advice and spiritual counsel, and through us,"},{"time":271911,"text":"my father was able to speak"},{"time":274451,"text":"and uplift,"},{"time":276645,"text":"letter by letter,"},{"time":278636,"text":"blink by blink."},{"time":281100,"text":"Everything in our world became slow and tender"},{"time":284992,"text":"as the din, drama and death of the hospital ward"},{"time":288356,"text":"faded into the background."},{"time":291860,"text":"I want to read to you one of the first things"},{"time":293960,"text":"that we transcribed in the week following the stroke."},{"time":298201,"text":"He composed a letter,"},{"time":300581,"text":"addressing his synagogue congregation,"},{"time":303202,"text":"and ended it with the following lines:"},{"time":306711,"text":"\"When my nape exploded,"},{"time":309190,"text":"I entered another dimension:"},{"time":311953,"text":"inchoate, sub-planetary, protozoan."},{"time":316610,"text":"Universes are opened and closed continually."},{"time":321199,"text":"There are many when low,"},{"time":323258,"text":"who stop growing."},{"time":325463,"text":"Last week, I was brought so low,"},{"time":327567,"text":"but I felt the hand of my father around me,"},{"time":331002,"text":"and my father brought me back.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":334422,"text":"When we weren't his voice,"},{"time":336667,"text":"we were his legs and arms."},{"time":340000,"text":"I moved them like I know I would have wanted"},{"time":342652,"text":"my own arms and legs to be moved"},{"time":345249,"text":"were they still for all the hours of the day."},{"time":349141,"text":"I remember I'd hold his fingers near my face,"},{"time":353124,"text":"bending each joint to keep it soft and limber."},{"time":357410,"text":"I'd ask him again and again"},{"time":359761,"text":"to visualize the motion,"},{"time":362258,"text":"to watch from within as the finger curled"},{"time":365779,"text":"and extended, and to move along with it"},{"time":369851,"text":"in his mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372562,"text":"Then, one day, from the corner of my eye,"},{"time":374575,"text":"I saw his body slither like a snake,"},{"time":378298,"text":"an involuntary spasm passing through the course"},{"time":381603,"text":"of his limbs."},{"time":383890,"text":"At first, I thought it was my own hallucination,"},{"time":386105,"text":"having spent so much time tending to this one body,"},{"time":389660,"text":"so desperate to see anything react on its own."},{"time":394320,"text":"But he told me he felt tingles,"},{"time":396980,"text":"sparks of electricity flickering on and off"},{"time":400515,"text":"just beneath the surface of the skin."},{"time":404272,"text":"The following week, he began ever so slightly"},{"time":407579,"text":"to show muscle resistance."},{"time":410335,"text":"Connections were being made."},{"time":412940,"text":"Body was slowly and gently reawakening,"},{"time":418164,"text":"limb by limb, muscle by muscle,"},{"time":421710,"text":"twitch by twitch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424641,"text":"As a documentary photographer,"},{"time":427278,"text":"I felt the need to photograph"},{"time":429080,"text":"each of his first movements"},{"time":431280,"text":"like a mother with her newborn."},{"time":433930,"text":"I photographed him taking his first unaided breath,"},{"time":438434,"text":"the celebratory moment after he showed"},{"time":441213,"text":"muscle resistance for the very first time,"},{"time":445220,"text":"the new adapted technologies that allowed him"},{"time":447930,"text":"to gain more and more independence."},{"time":451810,"text":"I photographed the care and the love"},{"time":453823,"text":"that surrounded him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464890,"text":"But my photographs only told the outside story"},{"time":468304,"text":"of a man lying in a hospital bed"},{"time":471616,"text":"attached to a breathing machine."},{"time":473270,"text":"I wasn't able to portray his story from within,"},{"time":476892,"text":"and so I began to search for a new visual language,"},{"time":480215,"text":"one which strived to express the ephemeral quality"},{"time":483513,"text":"of his spiritual experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506026,"text":"Finally, I want to share with you"},{"time":508284,"text":"a video from a series that I've been working on"},{"time":511642,"text":"that tries to express the slow, in-between existence"},{"time":514910,"text":"that my father has experienced."},{"time":517620,"text":"As he began to regain his ability to breathe,"},{"time":521170,"text":"I started recording his thoughts,"},{"time":523802,"text":"and so the voice that you hear in this video"},{"time":525726,"text":"is his voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528336,"text":"(Video) Ronnie Cahana: You have to believe"},{"time":531418,"text":"you're paralyzed"},{"time":534152,"text":"to play the part"},{"time":536907,"text":"of a quadriplegic."},{"time":542140,"text":"I don't."},{"time":544108,"text":"In my mind,"},{"time":546694,"text":"and in my dreams"},{"time":549456,"text":"every night"},{"time":552296,"text":"I Chagall-man float"},{"time":557211,"text":"over the city"},{"time":560339,"text":"twirl and swirl"},{"time":563556,"text":"with my toes kissing the floor."},{"time":571475,"text":"I know nothing about the statement"},{"time":578382,"text":"of man without motion."},{"time":584175,"text":"Everything has motion."},{"time":587799,"text":"The heart pumps."},{"time":591150,"text":"The body heaves."},{"time":595446,"text":"The mouth moves."},{"time":600160,"text":"We never stagnate."},{"time":604231,"text":"Life triumphs up and down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":611055,"text":"Kitra Cahana: For most of us,"},{"time":613131,"text":"our muscles begin to twitch and move"},{"time":615865,"text":"long before we are conscious,"},{"time":618373,"text":"but my father tells me his privilege"},{"time":621290,"text":"is living on the far periphery"},{"time":623469,"text":"of the human experience."},{"time":626472,"text":"Like an astronaut who sees a perspective"},{"time":629104,"text":"that very few of us will ever get to share,"},{"time":632322,"text":"he wonders and watches as he takes"},{"time":635428,"text":"his first breaths"},{"time":637305,"text":"and dreams about crawling back home."},{"time":641344,"text":"So begins life at 57, he says."},{"time":645123,"text":"A toddler has no attitude in its being,"},{"time":648622,"text":"but a man insists on his world every day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654325,"text":"Few of us will ever have to face physical limitations"},{"time":657970,"text":"to the degree that my father has,"},{"time":660928,"text":"but we will all have moments of paralysis"},{"time":664079,"text":"in our lives."},{"time":666440,"text":"I know I frequently confront walls"},{"time":669658,"text":"that feel completely unscalable,"},{"time":672897,"text":"but my father insists"},{"time":675157,"text":"that there are no dead ends."},{"time":678030,"text":"Instead, he invites me into his space of co-healing"},{"time":683240,"text":"to give the very best of myself, and for him"},{"time":686844,"text":"to give the very best of himself to me."},{"time":690274,"text":"Paralysis was an opening for him."},{"time":693311,"text":"It was an opportunity to emerge,"},{"time":695662,"text":"to rekindle life force,"},{"time":697856,"text":"to sit still long enough with himself"},{"time":699890,"text":"so as to fall in love with the full continuum"},{"time":703200,"text":"of creation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":705494,"text":"Today, my father is no longer locked in."},{"time":709476,"text":"He moves his neck with ease,"},{"time":712637,"text":"has had his feeding peg removed,"},{"time":715368,"text":"breathes with his own lungs,"},{"time":718150,"text":"speaks slowly with his own quiet voice,"},{"time":721634,"text":"and works every day"},{"time":723938,"text":"to gain more movement in his paralyzed body."},{"time":729148,"text":"But the work will never be finished."},{"time":731499,"text":"As he says, \"I'm living in a broken world,"},{"time":736212,"text":"and there is holy work to do.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":739243,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":741263,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}